CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Flash Newspicture Magazine, May 17, 1938, pg. 14 and 15, reads: "Activities Week at Pittsburgh's Y.M.C.A. - The Latimer players presented a play Thursday nite. (Photos by 'Teenie' Harris)."
TitMainTitle: Women and men of Latimer Players performing play, including woman seated in rocking chair with head down and holding cane, possibly in YMCA
